parameters:
\SE[17]Finally... it's almost time, right? \SE[12]Are you
ready...?
Panties are neatly displayed on the table...
\SE[70]... Huh? Why are there panties in a place like this?

\SE[0] When I said I didn't have any panties, Vita blushed and
gave them to me. \SE[1] So, because they were cute, I thought I'd
display them.

\SE[71] You don't have any 'panties'...? Are you displaying them
because they're cute...?

\SE[23] They have frills and they're so lovely, aren't they?
\!\SE[68] But I wonder what the 'theory' is for displaying
them.... \. I have no idea how to efficiently use 'panties' at
all....\SE[69]

\SE[70] The 'theory' of panties...? An efficient way to use
them...?

\SE[68]Um... If you want, I can give them to you. Panties.
\SE[48]They're cute, so I'm sure you'll like them...?

\SE[60] Eh, ah... Was it... bothersome? If that's the case, I
won't force it... They take up space... \SE[45] ... I'm feeling a
bit down...

\SE[70]Eh, ah...!!? If that's the case, then maybe I'll take
them... \SE[44]I really like cute things! U-um, I'm happy...!

\SE[12]I-I didn't give you the panties because I wanted you to be
happy or anything...! \!\SE[34]Don't misunderstand...! It's
bothersome, you know...!
